status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
goal
\end_layout

\end_inset

In this paper, our goal is to investigate the origins of this Ehrenfest
 failure by analyzing the underlying mixed quantum–classical theory; even
 more importantly we will propose a new 
\emph on
ad
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset

hoc
\emph default
 algorithm for adding spontaneous emission into an Ehrenfest framework.
\end_layout

