 According to the definition of bound charge (
\begin_inset Formula $\rho=-\boldsymbol{\nabla}\cdot\mathbf{P}$
\end_inset

) and the continuity equation (
\begin_inset Formula $\dot{\rho}+\boldsymbol{\nabla}\cdot\mathbf{J}=0$
\end_inset

