\begin_inset Formula $\widehat{\mathbf{P}}\left(\mathbf{r}\right)=\boldsymbol{\xi}\left(\mathbf{r}\right)\left(\left|0\right\rangle \left\langle 1\right|+\left|1\right\rangle \left\langle 0\right|\right)$
