\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{P}\left(\mathbf{r},t\right)=\text{Tr}_{s}\left\{ \widehat{\rho}\left(t\right)\widehat{\mathbf{P}}\left(\mathbf{r}\right)\right\} $
\end_inset

